import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { CommonModule } from '@angular/common'; import { RouterModule } from '@angular/router'; @Component({ selector: 'app-home', standalone: true, imports: [CommonModule, RouterModule], template: `
LeaveFlow

Leave Management
Simplified

Streamline your team's leave requests, approvals, and time-off tracking with our intuitive platform. Trusted by thousands of organizations worldwide.

Easy Request Management

Submit and approve leave requests with an intuitive interface that makes time-off management effortless.

Automated Approvals

Streamline approval workflow that saves time for managers and employees with intelligent automation.

Analytics & Insights

Track leave patterns and generate reports for better workforce planning and decision-making.

Ready to Transform Your Leave Management?

Join thousands of organizations already using LeaveFlow to streamline their HR processes.

© 2024 LeaveFlow. All rights reserved.

`, styles: [` .feature-card { text-align: center; padding: 2rem; background: white; border-radius: 1rem; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; transition: all 0.3s ease; } .feature-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); } .feature-icon { width: 4rem; height: 4rem; border-radius: 1rem; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin: 0 auto 1.5rem auto; } .bg-purple-100 { background-color: #f3f4f6; background-color: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.1); } .bg-green-100 { background-color: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.1); } .bg-blue-100 { background-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1); } .text-green-600 { color: #059669; } .text-blue-600 { color: #2563eb; } @media (max-width: 768px) { h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; } .grid-cols-1 { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } } `] }) export class HomeComponent {}
